---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import { posts } from '../data/blog'
---

<Layout title="Me and AI — UX Designer Orchestrating Human-AI Collaboration | Pablo Suzarte" description="How a Senior UX Designer designs environments where humans and AI collaborate. Project Intelligence, AI orchestration, workshops, and real projects." lang="en">
  <header class="hub-nav">
    <div class="hub-nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="hub-back">&larr; Portfolio</a>
      <a href="/" class="hub-logo">PS</a>
      <span class="hub-breadcrumb">Me and AI</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="hub">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hub-hero">
      <div class="hub-container hub-hero__inner">
        <div class="hub-hero__text">
          <p class="hub-kicker">The full picture</p>
          <h1 class="hub-title">Me and AI</h1>
          <p class="hub-subtitle">I design environments where humans and AI think together. This page connects everything: the mindset, the method, the tools, the proof, and the teaching.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hub-hero__photo">
          <img src="/pablo_profile_photo.png" alt="Pablo Suzarte" loading="eager" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- EXPLORE GRID -->
    <nav class="hub-explore" aria-label="Page sections">
      <div class="hub-container">
        <div class="hub-explore__grid">
          <a href="#philosophy" class="hub-explore__card">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            <h3>Project Intelligence</h3>
            <p>8 principles for designing how humans and AI work together</p>
          </a>
          <a href="#method" class="hub-explore__card">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
            <h3>Method</h3>
            <p>From idea to live site in one conversation</p>
          </a>
          <a href="#tools" class="hub-explore__card">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="4 17 10 11 4 5"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="20" y2="19"></line></svg>
            <h3>My AI Toolkit</h3>
            <p>Claude, ChatGPT, Gemini, Copilot, Terminal</p>
          </a>
          <a href="#projects" class="hub-explore__card">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
            <h3>Projects</h3>
            <p>3 live products built solo with AI</p>
          </a>
          <a href="#learn" class="hub-explore__card">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
            <h3>Learn</h3>
            <p>Workshops and courses to go from prompting to orchestrating</p>
          </a>
          <a href="#writing" class="hub-explore__card">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 3a2.85 2.85 0 1 1 4 4L7.5 20.5 2 22l1.5-5.5Z"/><path d="m15 5 4 4"/></svg>
            <h3>Writing</h3>
            <p>Essays on shared cognition and AI collaboration</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- 01 PHILOSOPHY -->
    <section id="philosophy" class="hub-section">
      <div class="hub-container">
        <span class="hub-num">01</span>
        <h2 class="hub-heading">Project Intelligence</h2>
        <p class="hub-lead">Most people prompt a chatbot. I design the conditions where humans and AI think together. Project Intelligence is the practice of structuring context, continuity, and collaboration so AI becomes a real partner, not just a tool you talk to.</p>

        <div class="hub-principles">
          <h3 class="hub-sub">8 Project Intelligence Principles</h3>
          <div class="hub-grid hub-grid--4">
            <div class="hub-card hub-card--principle" style="--card-accent: #D97757;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#D97757" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 10 10H12V2z"/><path d="M20 12a8 8 0 0 0-8-8v8h8z"/></svg>
              <strong>Shared memory</strong><p>AI needs to understand the project, why it matters, and what must not be misunderstood.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hub-card hub-card--principle" style="--card-accent: #5AAAFF;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#5AAAFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
              <strong>Current orientation</strong><p>A visible sense of where things stand: agreed, open, next.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hub-card hub-card--principle" style="--card-accent: #3EE0A5;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#3EE0A5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/></svg>
              <strong>Evidence discipline</strong><p>Ideas grounded in evidence, not assumptions or storytelling.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hub-card hub-card--principle" style="--card-accent: #FF9F43;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#FF9F43" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h5l2 3h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
              <strong>Asset awareness</strong><p>Both humans and AI know what materials exist.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hub-card hub-card--principle" style="--card-accent: #B49AFF;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#B49AFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
              <strong>Collaboration clarity</strong><p>How to work together well, not just what the project is about.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hub-card hub-card--principle" style="--card-accent: #64D2FF;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#64D2FF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
              <strong>Decision continuity</strong><p>Decisions preserved so the team does not restart the same thinking.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hub-card hub-card--principle" style="--card-accent: #FF85A1;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#FF85A1" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
              <strong>Role clarity</strong><p>Every collaborator, human or AI, has a clear role.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hub-card hub-card--principle" style="--card-accent: #FFD166;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#FFD166" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
              <strong>Reusable patterns</strong><p>Workflows that work are saved, refined, and reused.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hub-parallels">
          <h3 class="hub-sub">Same skill. New material.</h3>
          <div class="hub-parallel-list">
            <div class="hub-parallel"><span class="hub-parallel-label">Service Design</span><p>Makes complex experiences understandable.</p></div>
            <div class="hub-parallel-eq">=</div>
            <div class="hub-parallel"><span class="hub-parallel-label">Project Intelligence</span><p>Makes complex projects understandable.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 02 METHOD -->
    <section id="method" class="hub-section hub-section--alt">
      <div class="hub-container">
        <span class="hub-num">02</span>
        <h2 class="hub-heading">The method</h2>
        <p class="hub-lead">From idea to live site in one conversation. I set up project intelligence structures — CLAUDE.md files, agent roles, shared memory, and reusable workflows — that turn a chatbot conversation into a coordinated system of agents.</p>

        <div class="hub-steps">
          <div class="hub-step">
            <span class="hub-step-num">1</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Describe the vision</strong>
              <p>Be specific about what you want, how it should feel, who it is for.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hub-step">
            <span class="hub-step-num">2</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Set up the environment</strong>
              <p>CLAUDE.md, agent roles, memory files, permissions. This is the project intelligence layer.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hub-step">
            <span class="hub-step-num">3</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Orchestrate and build</strong>
              <p>AI reads, plans, implements, tests. You guide with feedback and judgment.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hub-step">
            <span class="hub-step-num">4</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Ship</strong>
              <p>Commit, push, deploy. Live in minutes, not weeks.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/how-i-build-with-ai" class="hub-cta">See the full method &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 03 TOOLS -->
    <section id="tools" class="hub-section">
      <div class="hub-container">
        <span class="hub-num">03</span>
        <h2 class="hub-heading">My AI toolkit</h2>
        <p class="hub-lead">I focus on simplicity and speed. Each tool has a clear role. The skill is not mastering one platform. It is knowing which one fits the problem and moving fast.</p>

        <!-- Terminal: full width on top -->
        <div class="hub-card hub-card--tool hub-card--featured">
          <div class="hub-tool-header">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="4 17 10 11 4 5"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="20" y2="19"></line></svg>
            <strong>Terminal</strong>
          </div>
          <p>Where the orchestration happens. I work directly in the command line, running AI agents, managing git, and deploying to production. This is the control centre.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 2x2 grid: AI tools -->
        <div class="hub-grid hub-grid--2">
          <div class="hub-card hub-card--tool">
            <div class="hub-tool-header">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="var(--accent)" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m4.7144 15.9555 4.7174-2.6471.079-.2307-.079-.1275h-.2307l-.7893-.0486-2.6956-.0729-2.3375-.0971-2.2646-.1214-.5707-.1215-.5343-.7042.0546-.3522.4797-.3218.686.0608 1.5179.1032 2.2767.1578 1.6514.0972 2.4468.255h.3886l.0546-.1579-.1336-.0971-.1032-.0972L6.973 9.8356l-2.55-1.6879-1.3356-.9714-.7225-.4918-.3643-.4614-.1578-1.0078.6557-.7225.8803.0607.2246.0607.8925.686 1.9064 1.4754 2.4893 1.8336.3643.3035.1457-.1032.0182-.0728-.164-.2733-1.3539-2.4467-1.445-2.4893-.6435-1.032-.17-.6194c-.0607-.255-.1032-.4674-.1032-.7285L6.287.1335 6.6997 0l.9957.1336.419.3642.6192 1.4147 1.0018 2.2282 1.5543 3.0296.4553.8985.2429.8318.091.255h.1579v-.1457l.1275-1.706.2368-2.0947.2307-2.6957.0789-.7589.3764-.9107.7468-.4918.5828.2793.4797.686-.0668.4433-.2853 1.8517-.5586 2.9021-.3643 1.9429h.2125l.2429-.2429.9835-1.3053 1.6514-2.0643.7286-.8196.85-.9046.5464-.4311h1.0321l.759 1.1293-.34 1.1657-1.0625 1.3478-.8804 1.1414-1.2628 1.7-.7893 1.36.0729.1093.1882-.0183 2.8535-.607 1.5421-.2794 1.8396-.3157.8318.3886.091.3946-.3278.8075-1.967.4857-2.3072.4614-3.4364.8136-.0425.0304.0486.0607 1.5482.1457.6618.0364h1.621l3.0175.2247.7892.522.4736.6376-.079.4857-1.2142.6193-1.6393-.3886-3.825-.9107-1.3113-.3279h-.1822v.1093l1.0929 1.0686 2.0035 1.8092 2.5075 2.3314.1275.5768-.3218.4554-.34-.0486-2.2039-1.6575-.85-.7468-1.9246-1.621h-.1275v.17l.4432.6496 2.3436 3.5214.1214 1.0807-.17.3521-.6071.2125-.6679-.1214-1.3721-1.9246L14.38 17.959l-1.1414-1.9428-.1397.079-.674 7.2552-.3156.3703-.7286.2793-.6071-.4614-.3218-.7468.3218-1.4753.3886-1.9246.3157-1.53.2853-1.9004.17-.6314-.0121-.0425-.1397.0182-1.4328 1.9672-2.1796 2.9446-1.7243 1.8456-.4128.164-.7164-.3704.0667-.6618.4008-.5889 2.386-3.0357 1.4389-1.882.929-1.0868-.0062-.1579h-.0546l-6.3385 4.1164-1.1293.1457-.4857-.4554.0608-.7467.2307-.2429 1.9064-1.3114Z"/></svg>
              <strong>Claude &amp; Claude Code</strong>
            </div>
            <p>My primary partner. Deep reasoning, multi-step orchestration, and building full applications from intent.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hub-card hub-card--tool">
            <div class="hub-tool-header">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 256 260" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M239.184 106.203a64.716 64.716 0 0 0-5.576-53.103C219.452 28.459 191 15.784 163.213 21.74A65.586 65.586 0 0 0 52.096 45.22a64.716 64.716 0 0 0-43.23 31.36 65.586 65.586 0 0 0 8.031 76.74 64.716 64.716 0 0 0 5.525 53.102c14.174 24.65 42.644 37.324 70.446 31.36a65.586 65.586 0 0 0 111.117-23.56 64.716 64.716 0 0 0 43.23-31.36 65.586 65.586 0 0 0-8.031-76.66Zm-97.56 136.338a48.397 48.397 0 0 1-31.105-11.255l1.535-.87 51.67-29.825a8.595 8.595 0 0 0 4.247-7.367v-72.85l21.845 12.636c.218.111.37.32.409.563v60.367c-.056 26.818-21.783 48.545-48.601 48.6ZM37.158 197.93a48.345 48.345 0 0 1-5.781-32.589l1.534.921 51.722 29.826a8.339 8.339 0 0 0 8.441 0l63.181-36.425v25.221a.717.717 0 0 1-.358.665l-52.335 30.184c-23.257 13.398-52.97 5.431-66.404-17.803ZM23.549 85.38a48.499 48.499 0 0 1 25.58-21.333v59.39a8.288 8.288 0 0 0 4.195 7.316l62.874 36.272-21.845 12.636a.718.718 0 0 1-.767 0L41.353 149.48c-23.211-13.454-31.171-43.144-17.804-64.1Zm180.465 41.695-63.08-36.63L162.78 77.81a.718.718 0 0 1 .768 0l52.233 30.184a48.652 48.652 0 0 1-7.316 87.635v-61.391a8.544 8.544 0 0 0-4.45-7.862Zm21.742-32.69-1.535-.922-51.619-30.081a8.39 8.39 0 0 0-8.492 0L100.981 99.64V74.42a.716.716 0 0 1 .307-.665l52.233-30.133a48.652 48.652 0 0 1 72.236 50.391v.372ZM88.061 139.098l-21.845-12.585a.716.716 0 0 1-.358-.665V65.685a48.652 48.652 0 0 1 79.757-37.346l-1.535.87-51.67 29.825a8.595 8.595 0 0 0-4.246 7.367l-.103 72.697Zm11.868-25.58L128.067 97.3l28.188 16.218v32.434l-28.086 16.218-28.24-16.218v-32.434Z"/></svg>
              <strong>ChatGPT &amp; Codex</strong>
            </div>
            <p>Fast exploration and rapid prototyping. Brainstorming ideas and quick conversational problem-solving.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hub-card hub-card--tool">
            <div class="hub-tool-header">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="url(#gemGradTool)" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.04 19.32Q12 21.51 12 24q0-2.49.93-4.68.96-2.19 2.58-3.81t3.81-2.55Q21.51 12 24 12q-2.49 0-4.68-.93a12.3 12.3 0 0 1-3.81-2.58 12.3 12.3 0 0 1-2.58-3.81Q12 2.49 12 0q0 2.49-.96 4.68-.93 2.19-2.55 3.81a12.3 12.3 0 0 1-3.81 2.58Q2.49 12 0 12q2.49 0 4.68.96 2.19.93 3.81 2.55t2.55 3.81"/><defs><linearGradient id="gemGradTool" x1="0" y1="0" x2="24" y2="24"><stop stop-color="#4285F4"/><stop offset=".5" stop-color="#886FBF"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#D96570"/></linearGradient></defs></svg>
              <strong>Google Gemini</strong>
            </div>
            <p>Multi-modal research across large documents and cross-referencing sources at scale.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hub-card hub-card--tool">
            <div class="hub-tool-header">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M23.922 16.997C23.061 18.492 18.063 22.02 12 22.02 5.937 22.02.939 18.492.078 16.997A.641.641 0 0 1 0 16.741v-2.869a.883.883 0 0 1 .053-.22c.372-.935 1.347-2.292 2.605-2.656.167-.429.414-1.055.644-1.517a10.098 10.098 0 0 1-.052-1.086c0-1.331.282-2.499 1.132-3.368.397-.406.89-.717 1.474-.952C7.255 2.937 9.248 1.98 11.978 1.98c2.731 0 4.767.957 6.166 2.093.584.235 1.077.546 1.474.952.85.869 1.132 2.037 1.132 3.368 0 .368-.014.733-.052 1.086.23.462.477 1.088.644 1.517 1.258.364 2.233 1.721 2.605 2.656a.841.841 0 0 1 .053.22v2.869a.641.641 0 0 1-.078.256Zm-11.75-5.992h-.344a4.359 4.359 0 0 1-.355.508c-.77.947-1.918 1.492-3.508 1.492-1.725 0-2.989-.359-3.782-1.259a2.137 2.137 0 0 1-.085-.104L4 11.746v6.585c1.435.779 4.514 2.179 8 2.179 3.486 0 6.565-1.4 8-2.179v-6.585l-.098-.104s-.033.045-.085.104c-.793.9-2.057 1.259-3.782 1.259-1.59 0-2.738-.545-3.508-1.492a4.359 4.359 0 0 1-.355-.508Zm2.328 3.25c.549 0 1 .451 1 1v2c0 .549-.451 1-1 1-.549 0-1-.451-1-1v-2c0-.549.451-1 1-1Zm-5 0c.549 0 1 .451 1 1v2c0 .549-.451 1-1 1-.549 0-1-.451-1-1v-2c0-.549.451-1 1-1Zm3.313-6.185c.136 1.057.403 1.913.878 2.497.442.544 1.134.938 2.344.938 1.573 0 2.292-.337 2.657-.751.384-.435.558-1.15.558-2.361 0-1.14-.243-1.847-.705-2.319-.477-.488-1.319-.862-2.824-1.025-1.487-.161-2.192.138-2.533.529-.269.307-.437.808-.438 1.578v.021c0 .265.021.562.063.893Zm-1.626 0c.042-.331.063-.628.063-.894v-.02c-.001-.77-.169-1.271-.438-1.578-.341-.391-1.046-.69-2.533-.529-1.505.163-2.347.537-2.824 1.025-.462.472-.705 1.179-.705 2.319 0 1.211.175 1.926.558 2.361.365.414 1.084.751 2.657.751 1.21 0 1.902-.394 2.344-.938.475-.584.742-1.44.878-2.497Z"/></svg>
              <strong>Microsoft Copilot</strong>
            </div>
            <p>AI pair programmer inside the IDE. Context-aware suggestions that keep you in flow while writing and refactoring.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hub-card hub-card--tool">
            <div class="hub-tool-header">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M24 22.525H0l12-21.05 12 21.05z"/></svg>
              <strong>Vercel</strong>
            </div>
            <p>Instant deployments. Every push goes live automatically. The bridge between code and production.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hub-card hub-card--tool">
            <div class="hub-tool-header">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 0C5.374 0 0 5.373 0 12c0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23A11.509 11.509 0 0 1 12 5.803c1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576C20.566 21.797 24 17.3 24 12c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
